zxr10shelfTable.name: zxr10shelfTable
zxr10shelfTable.description: the description of zxr10 shelf infomation it is a list of shelf entries.

zxr10shelfEntry.name: zxr10shelfEntry
zxr10shelfEntry.description: A shelf entry containing objects that descript the shelf infomation,such as: zxr10ShelfRackNo,zxr10ShelfNo , zxr10ShelfAttrib,zxr10ShelfAvailStatus.

zxr10ShelfNo.name: zxr10ShelfNo
zxr10ShelfNo.description: the no. of the special shelf.

zxr10ShelfAttrib.name: zxr10ShelfAttrib
zxr10ShelfAttrib.description: the attribute. of the special rack. eg ,the current shelf is a working shelf, we use 1,else if the shelf is a fan shelf we use 2 ,etc.

zxr10ShelfAvailStatus.name: zxr10ShelfAvailStatus
zxr10ShelfAvailStatus.description: the status. of the special shelf. eg ,the current shelf is in use, we use 1,else if the shelfis unuse, we use 0 .

zxr10portTable.name: zxr10portTable
zxr10portTable.description: the description of port infomation in the zxr10 card . it is a list of port entries.

zxr10portEntry.name: zxr10portEntry
zxr10portEntry.description: A port entry containing objects that descript the port infomation,such as: zxr10PortNo zxr10PortType zxr10PortWorkingType zxr10PortMTU zxr10PortSpeed zxr10PortAvailStatus zxr10PortOperStatus.

zxr10PortIfIndex.name: zxr10PortIfIndex
zxr10PortIfIndex.description: the IfIndex of the port on the card.

zxr10PortNo.name: zxr10PortNo
zxr10PortNo.description: the no. of the port on the card, which contains several ports .

zxr10PortType.name: zxr10PortType
zxr10PortType.description: the type of the port.such as: fei : Fast Ethernet Interface gei : Gigabit Ethernet Interface card oc3 : Optic Cable 3 interface card oc12 : Optic Cable 12 interface card oc48 : Optic Cable 48 interface card atm155 : atm155 interface card .

zxr10PortWorkingType.name: zxr10PortWorkingType
zxr10PortWorkingType.description: auto-config(0) indicate the port working type is auto-config, full-duplex(1) indicate the port working type is full duplex, half-duplex(2) indicate the port working type is half duplex.

zxr10PortSpeed.name: zxr10PortSpeed
zxr10PortSpeed.description: the transmit speed of this port, unit is Mbps.

zxr10PortAvailStatus.name: zxr10PortAvailStatus
zxr10PortAvailStatus.description: the status. of the special port. eg ,the current port is running, we use 1,else if the card is down, we use 0 . 1 indicate physical level initialize ok 0 indicate physical level initialize not ok

zxr10PortOperStatus.name: zxr10PortOperStatus
zxr10PortOperStatus.description: the operstatus. of the special card. eg ,the current card can work, we use 1, else if the card can't,we use 0 . for upc board: 1 indicate mpu and rpu both run normally, 0 indicate error, for sfc npc board: 1 indicate upc communicate with them(sfc,upc) normally, 0 indicate error.
